com.ahok.cuber.controller

Class TripController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ahok.cuber.controller.TripController

  • @RestController
public class TripController
extends java.lang.Object
    Rest CRUD Trip Controller

    Available endpoints:

    • GET trips/all Get a list of all Trips
    • GET trips/get/{id} Get Trip by id
    • POST trips/add Add new Trip
    • PUT trips/update Update Trip
    • DELETE trips/delete/{id} Delete Trip
